pulltitle: Remove mention of email address in user()
pullsbody: I was trying to use the `user()` method yesterday w/ an email address to no avail. When I talked to @cadecairos on IRC, he said he had to change the method to not support email addresses, so I'm updating the docs now.
pull_commit_message:
Remove mention of email address in user()

I was trying to use the `user()` method yesterday w/ an email address to no avail. When I talked to cade on IRC, he said he had to change the method to not support email addresses, so I'm updating the docs now.
